{"tid":483554,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"一個可怕的觸電經歷，膽小者勿入","createTime":"2017-11-29T08:19:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-01T09:46:55.000Z","uid":38539,"like":2,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c309e040af928abb063c41c26075ae7ce2c43bd2","tid":483554,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T08:19:55.000Z","msg":"我記得個一日好憤怒 原因並唔重要<br />\n重要的係個一刻 我好憤怒<br />\n交感神經系統控制腎上腺素的釋放<br />\n令我身體條件反射打出一個直拳<br />\n面前的燈曲掣被我一拳擊碎<br />\n瞬間冒出微弱的火花<br />\n我感到一股強力的電流纏繞住身體<br />\n然後施然地離開<br />\n<br />\n吓 你問我點解無事？<br />\n可能因為我份人膠膠哋掛 ( 笑 )"},{"pid":"1ee3a93033bfe89e510047242308ef30994388af","tid":483554,"uid":22946,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T08:26:02.000Z","msg":"屌係老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9a64d10c9ba3d451038d33975b089f84a53d608","tid":483554,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T08:45:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e687bea33a9bb5e009a3063210131aa0b824368b","tid":483554,"uid":70760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T08:47:53.000Z","msg":"觸電導致有憤怒感覺?"},{"pid":"87cd7f4554d72dbf900338f56646a0999ac3d170","tid":483554,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T10:51:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>觸電導致有憤怒感覺?</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c5c92a7faeccc8e2caa32b08735e409713a76e3","tid":483554,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T13:54:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c00d90121f4daf74af3eaf00fe2dc9c7d5eae970","tid":483554,"uid":5921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T13:55:08.000Z","msg":"超級撒亞人？"},{"pid":"70384f26e3f4a4c914d7ff97a8b3590f6d70a483","tid":483554,"uid":9699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB